ead()f.close()clientSocket.sendto(image_data, (server_name, server_port))modifiedImage, serverAddress = clientSocket.recvfrom(20480)xjtlu2 = open('/Users/chenzhengde/PycharmProjects/CAN201Lab3/xjtlu2.jpg', 'wb')xjtlu2.write(modifiedImage)xjtlu2.close()clientSocket.close() Reference XJTLU slides (Week3)
